#. 2: reset_colour
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_Desc"
msgid ""
"Hudson, Bolson Construction's veteran\n"
"carpenter, has departed for the <1.se_co>Akkala<2.re_co>\n"
"region to expand the business.\n"
"\n"
"Akkala is far to the north of Hateno Village.\n"
"If you happen to be passing by, stop in and\n"
"pay <3.se_co>Hudson<4.re_co> a visit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_Finish"
msgid ""
"Hudson and Rhondson are happily married, and\n"
"Tarrey Town is enjoying great prosperity.\n"
"\n"
"As a sign of appreciation for bringing the town\n"
"together and as compensation for your work,\n"
"Hudson gave you a hefty amount of gems that\n"
"were unearthed during the town's construction.\n"
"\n"
"You wished the couple eternal happiness before\n"
"heading on your way."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_Invite01"
msgid ""
"Greyson the Goron has moved to Tarrey Town,\n"
"and his younger brother Pelison tagged along\n"
"for the ride.\n"
"\n"
"Pay the town a visit to make sure they\n"
"arrived safely, and check in with <1.se_co>Hudson<2.re_co>\n"
"while you're there."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_Invite02"
msgid ""
"A Gerudo by the name of Rhondson has moved\n"
"to Tarrey Town.\n"
"\n"
"Pay the town a visit to make sure she arrived\n"
"safely. Check in with <1.se_co>Hudson <2.re_co>while you're there."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_Invite03"
msgid ""
"A Rito by the name of Fyson has moved to\n"
"Tarrey Town to run the general store.\n"
"\n"
"Pay the town a visit to make sure he arrived\n"
"safely, and check in with <1.se_co>Hudson <2.re_co>while\n"
"you're there."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_Invite04"
msgid ""
"A former Zora priest by the name of Kapson\n"
"has moved to Tarrey Town!\n"
"\n"
"Pay the town a visit to make sure he arrived\n"
"safely and to see what other shenanigans\n"
"<1.se_co>Hudson <2.re_co>has been up to. There's always\n"
"something going on with that guy!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_Invite05"
msgid ""
"Bolson and Karson departed for Tarrey Town.\n"
"\n"
"All that's left now is to return to the town\n"
"yourself and enjoy Hudson and Rhondson's\n"
"wedding ceremony!\n"
"\n"
"Head back to the town and look for <1.se_co>Hudson<2.re_co>."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_LookFor01"
msgid ""
"You brought Hudson enough wood to get him\n"
"started, but now he needs to break the boulders\n"
"scattered across the future site of Tarrey Town.\n"
"He's asked you to find a <1.se_co>Goron <2.re_co>strong enough\n"
"to help out.\n"
"\n"
"According to the Bolson Construction hiring\n"
"guidelines, you need to seek out <3.se_co>a Goron\n"
"whose name ends in \"son.\"<4.re_co> The guidelines are\n"
"unusually specific about this."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_LookFor02"
msgid ""
"You delivered more wood to Hudson.\n"
"\n"
"But now he needs someone who can mend his\n"
"work clothes. He wants you to find a <1.se_co>Gerudo<2.re_co>\n"
"skilled at sewing, but remember the stipulation\n"
"in the Bolson Construction hiring guidelines:\n"
"the <3.se_co>Gerudo's name must end in \"son.\"<4.re_co>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_LookFor03"
msgid ""
"You brought Hudson more wood.\n"
"\n"
"His next goal is to open up a general store and\n"
"trade routes, and he thinks a <1.se_co>Rito <2.re_co>merchant\n"
"would be perfect for the job.\n"
"\n"
"Find a Rito with the know-how to manage a\n"
"shop and the connections to set up trade,\n"
"and of course, make sure <3.se_co>his or her name\n"
"ends in \"son.\"<4.re_co>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_LookFor04"
msgid ""
"You brought Hudson enough wood!\n"
"\n"
"And now, as it turns out, Hudson is engaged to\n"
"Rhondson! Can you believe it?\n"
"\n"
"They want to hold a ceremony, so he wants you\n"
"to find a <1.se_co>Zora <2.re_co>who can officiate. Even though\n"
"this Zora technically won't be working for\n"
"Hudson's company, he would be much more\n"
"comfortable if the <3.se_co>Zora's name ended in \"son.\"<4.re_co>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_LookFor05"
msgid ""
"Kapson, a Zora and former priest, arrived safely\n"
"in Tarrey Town and began making preparations\n"
"for the wedding ceremony.\n"
"\n"
"Hudson wants to invite Bolson and Karson to\n"
"his wedding, but he's too busy with preparations\n"
"of his own. Go to <1.se_co>Hateno Village <2.re_co>to invite "
"<3.se_co>Bolson\n"
"and Karson<4.re_co>."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_Marry"
msgid ""
"Hudson and Rhondson's wedding was a shining\n"
"beacon in an otherwise dark, dangerous world.\n"
"\n"
"Rhondson was a little taken aback by a few of\n"
"the vows, but everything worked out fine and is\n"
"in perfect compliance with Bolson Construction's\n"
"guidelines.\n"
"\n"
"It's only polite to give your blessing to the lovely\n"
"couple who just vowed their undying love, so go\n"
"talk to <1.se_co>Hudson<2.re_co>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_Name"
msgid "From the Ground Up"
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_Wood01"
msgid ""
"You bumped into Hudson in the Akkala region,\n"
"and it sounds like he plans on building a town\n"
"there as a part of Bolson Construction's\n"
"expansion. He even has a name picked out—it\n"
"will be known as Tarrey Town. That said, he is\n"
"missing a few things required to make a town.\n"
"\n"
"You know, small things—like lumber.\n"
"\n"
"Bring him <1.se_co>10 bundles of wood<2.re_co> to get\n"
"him started."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_Wood02"
msgid ""
"Greyson and Pelison arrived safely in\n"
"Tarrey Town and got right to work. Greyson\n"
"is breaking apart the boulders, and Pelison\n"
"is selling the ore they find within.\n"
"\n"
"Hudson wants to build some more buildings, but\n"
"he needs more material. <1.se_co>Twenty bundles of\n"
"wood<2.re_co> should hold him over for this next bunch\n"
"of buildings."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_Wood03"
msgid ""
"Rhondson arrived safely in Tarrey Town and got\n"
"right to work. She is not only mending work\n"
"clothes—she also opened up an armor shop!\n"
"\n"
"Hudson wants to build more buildings, but he's\n"
"run out of materials once again.\n"
"\n"
"Another <1.se_co>30 bundles of wood <2.re_co>should cover\n"
"him for now."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_UMiiMini_MakeVillage_Wood04"
msgid ""
"Fyson arrived safely in Tarrey Town and put\n"
"the experience he gained from running his\n"
"family's shop to good use. He opened up a\n"
"general store!\n"
"\n"
"Hudson wants to build another batch of\n"
"buildings, but he needs more material.\n"
"\n"
"Bring him another <1.se_co>50 bundles of wood<2.re_co>."
msgstr ""

